<DOCNO>WT18-B26-37</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA076-000510-B005-306</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.digmagazine.com:80/56-96/native.htm 207.158.234.90 19970124020852 text/html 5069
HTTP/1.1 200 OK
Date: Fri, 24 Jan 1997 02:08:47 GMT
Server: Apache/1.2b4
