<A HREF="/f/organs/index.html"><IMG SRC="/f/gif/organisations2.gif" BORDER=0  ALT="Organisations" ALIGN=RIGHT></A><ALIGN=BASELINE><H1>Dialogai</H1><HR>

<IMG ALIGN=right HSPACE=0 WIDTH=250 SRC="/gif/dialog_l.gif">
57 av. Wendt<BR>
(entr&eacute;e rue Liotard),<BR>
Case postale 27,<BR>
1211 Gen&egrave;ve 7<br>
<i>t&eacute;l&eacute;phone (022) 340 00 00,<BR> 

t&eacute;l&eacute;fax (022) 340 03 98</i><br clear>


<HR WIDTH=550>
<UL>



<LI><A HREF="#presentation">Pr&eacute;sentation</A> de Dialogai

<LI><A HREF="#phone">Permanence t&eacute;l&eacute;phonique, entretiens...</A>

