<HTML><HEAD>
<META name="description" content="Migrants against HIV/AIDS (Migrants contre le sida) Newsletter about AIDS organizing by Black and Third World communities in Europe">
<META name="keywords" content="AIDS, HIV, racism, race, racist, Third World, people of color, antiracism, fascism, Europe, Fortress Europe, SIDA, VIH, Arab, Black, African, Asian, Surinamese">
<TITLE>Migrants against HIV/AIDS Migrants contre le sida</TITLE></HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF">

<IMG SRC="http://www.hivnet.ch/migrants/cgi-bin/makelog.cgi?migrants_index,http://www.hivnet.ch/migrants/index.html" HEIGHT="1" WIDTH="1" ALIGN=LEFT>

