<HEAD><TITLE>INFOTHEQUE SIDA - Infoth&egrave;que SIDA 02/96</TITLE></HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="FFFFFF">
<A HREF="/f/search"><IMG ALIGN=RIGHT BORDER=0 SRC="/gif/Search2.gif"></A>
<A HREF="INFOTHEQUE.cgi?+9602"><IMG ALIGN=RIGHT BORDER=0 SRC="/gif/Bibliotheque2.gif"></A><IMG ALIGN=left BORDER=0 SRC="INFOTHEQUE/gif/marge.gif"><H2>AIDS INFOTHEK - INFOTHEQUE SIDA</H2><I>Das Magazin der Aids Info Docu Schweiz<BR>Le magazine de Sida Info Doc Suisse</I><BR CLEAR><p><center><b><i>On a constat&eacute; que toute infection "consomme", c'est-&agrave;-dire que l'organisme a besoin de davantage d'&eacute;nergie, de vitamines et de min&eacute;raux. Cela vaut aussi pour l'infection par le VIH.<br>Man hat festgestellt, dass jede Infektion "konsumierend" wirkt, das heisst, der K&ouml;rper braucht mehr Energie, Vitamine und Mineralstoffe. Das gilt auch f&uuml;r die HIV-Infektion.</i></b></center><p><CENTER>
<A HREF="INFOTHEQUE.cgi?9602:12.3"><IMG BORDER=0 SRC="/gif/left.gif"></A>
<A HREF="INFOTHEQUE.cgi?9602:13.1"><IMG BORDER=0 SRC="/gif/right.gif"></A>
</CENTER>
<UL>
<h3>HIV pre-test counselling. How to conduct pre-test counselling in confidence</h3><blockquote><b>Hygia Communications (Ed.), King's Health Care Trust (Ed.)</b><br><i>Bromley, 1995, 37 Min., £ 60.-- (mit Begleitmaterial)</i><p>Continuing public awareness about AIDS and HIV has led to increasing demands for HIV testing across a wide range of services. The test itself is simple, but the effect it can have on the client can be traumatic - so pre-test counselling is vital. With a large number of statutory and voluntary agencies outside mainstream sexual health now offering the test, it's essential that workers have the confidence and skills to conduct these tests properly. The purpose of this video is tho show the key issues which need to be addressed in pre-test counselling in order to gain the client's informed consent. The video is to be used with accompanying guide.<p><i>Alle vier Videos sind zu beziehen bei:<br>Video Sales Dept. Hygia Communications Ltd.<br>PO Box11; GB-Bromley BR2 7RW<br>Tel. 0044 81 289 9559 Fax. 0044 81 462 3206</i></blockquote></UL>
