<H3>AIDS Daily Summary - April 4, 1996</H3>
<I>Centers for Disease Control and Prevention Clearinghouse<BR>Copyright 1995, Information, Inc., Bethesda, MD</I>
<BR CLEAR><HR>
<CENTER>
<A HREF="SUMM-96.cgi?960404:9"><IMG BORDER=0 SRC="/gif/left.gif"></A>
